{"tid":2496783,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一名女子在上海車展向Tesla抗議被行政拘留5日","createTime":"2021-04-20T05:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T05:40:37.000Z","uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f58a30476cc1652f319f69173b9436486b63a2d0","tid":2496783,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:10:40.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】上海有一名女子到車展Tesla展區抗議，被行政拘留5日。<br />\n<br />\n一名穿上印有「剎車失靈」 T恤的女子，昨日在車展Tesla展台站在車頂上抗議，公司回應說，當事人是二月河南安陽發生超速事件的車主，之後以產品質量為由要求退回車輛，公司表示願意協助完成檢測、維修或保險賠償等事宜，但車主拒絕提出的解決方案，公司強調對不合理的訴求不會妥協 。<br />\n<br />\n上海警方發布通告，指涉事女子與另一名女子因為與公司有消費糾紛，強行爬上車頂造成車輛受損，因擾亂公共秩序，被處以行政拘留5日，另一人就被處以行政警告。"},{"pid":"b8b6ca989971c905ebc8c9cbeb92c80bdb368ca2","tid":2496783,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:10:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=431754\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D431754&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuAomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=7b3f0f9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D431754&h=21bc253d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=431754</a>"},{"pid":"6b924cfbd5f0fd30b38a283fab4e0f2bcbe6b545","tid":2496783,"uid":73627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59974fdaa98777ec40e761bb6f6abfc44dc46f1c","tid":2496783,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:32:57.000Z","msg":"早兩日先又有一單自動駕駛撞樹爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307a9c712413125c8cd17803cfe14255eee22b6f","tid":2496783,"uid":215755,"like":0,"di